{"tid":1780393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，都係第一次去寶福山","createTime":"2019-12-12T10:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T12:01:48.000Z","uid":110109,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"384535cef703dc7f37617b3b93f5bbce5720d0be","tid":1780393,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"我地永遠都無法代你去孝順周爸爸周媽媽<br />\n但係我地一定會堅持落去<br />\n一定會搵返真相<br />\n一定會打返一個你想要既香港返黎<br />\n<br />\n我應承你會做好我自己崗位<br />\n我會睇實身邊既手足、幫到就盡我全力幫<br />\n都唔會再比睇哨既手足再係咁樣身陷險境<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好對你唔住 我地真係做唔到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梓樂 願你在天堂安息<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRJP74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRJP74.jpg&h=dd4bc23e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02ff1b4f037ec19c49d36e9cfa4c754550bf38e7","tid":1780393,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />山上山下都有人龍<br />\n黎緊既手足盡快，未必走到去埋愛丁堡<br />\n所以揀一到去，i think both okay"},{"pid":"ded066352120ead0c63a875c4f370d21c7594771","tid":1780393,"uid":110109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"山上手足都請莊重啲唔好爛口 例如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc2aa618b0d334fcd68a5bf5601fcbf80dea8f","tid":1780393,"uid":36269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"希望大家見到xx 都忍口，專重手足"},{"pid":"7b6eb5cc3d07a21b1445731fc3319f09d9946f5f","tid":1780393,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"Me"},{"pid":"f278035b2478c742a7dce5b882b71a36ca1a8b91","tid":